{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She's just slipping on her blazer, over her shoulder holster.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She's furious.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: CLARICE
{DIALOGUE}: Chilton has killed her, hasn't he?
{DIALOGUE}: That slimy little bastard!
{DIALOGUE}: We were so close with Lecter - and now her last chance is gone.
